data.description: This home will not pass for VA or FHA. Please see agent to agent notes Must be cash or conventional.. Move in ready and affordable home.  Inviting front porch. Newer windows, some new paint, new flooring, in the  kitchen and appliances stay. Two full baths ( first floor includes shower and toilet, no sink). First floor bedroom. Plus two large upstairs bedrooms. Enclosed back porch (mudroom) has potential for first floor laundry. There is plenty of off street parking available in the front and back w/ double lot 45X90.  Possession at closing and funding.
